 - running - startedAt: 1776214507530\n4. `telegram:direct:6053576134` - Lead direct - running - startedAt: 1776212125325\n\nLooking at the previous report from 00:51 UTC, it was tracking cron:ed2d0b5d as the QLHV 5p monitor and cron:e7885813 as the Agent Status to Lead session.\n\nNow at 01:01 UTC, the same three cron sessions are still running with no new failures or blockers detected. I'm also noticing the DTLX 5p cron session (cron:6f3323ef) is still active, and I'm checking when it actually started to get a fuller picture of what's running.\n\nLooking at the session history from the earlier cron run, the DTLX 5p monitor appears to have been running since around 23:13 UTC, and the Lead direct session has been active for roughly 39 minutes. Comparing this to the previous status report at 00:51, the state seems consistent—same three cron sessions still running, nothing new has failed, and there are no additional blockers to report.\n\nNow I'm checking the status of the main session, which shows as done, and the daily briefing cron that ran around 23:16 UTC—it's completed normally as expected. The Lead direct session appears to still be running based on its recent activity timestamp.\n\nLet me recalculate the timing more carefully. The Lead direct session was started around 00:55 UTC, and the QLHV 5p session has been running for about 10 minutes since the 00:51 checkpoint.\n\nLooking at the status report that came through the Agent Status cron, I'm seeing three active sessions: the QLHV and DTLX 5p progress monitors plus the direct communication channel with the Lead. Everything appears to be running smoothly with no blockers or failures.\n\nSince the pipeline is healthy and no changes have occurred since the last report, I'll stay silent and update the heartbeat state file as instructed."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing against previous cron report (00:51 UTC):\n\n**Same 3 cron sessions running** — `cron:ed2d0b5d` (QLHV), `cron:e7885813` (Agent Status), `cron:6f3323ef` (DTLX). No new failures, no blockers, no session changes.\n\n**Silent exit — pipeline stable.** Updating heartbeat state only.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q9pitsf3rroq_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json","content":"{\n  \"lastChecked\": \"2026-04-15T01:01:00Z\",\n  \"sessions\": {\n    \"cron:ed2d0b5d\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"5p QLHV monitor\", \"note\": \"running ~10m since 00:51 UTC\" },\n    \"cron:e7885813\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Agent Status to Lead\", \"note\": \"running ~10m since 00:51 UTC\" },\n    \"cron:6f3323ef\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"DTLX 5p Monitor\", \"note\": \"running ~7h 48m since ~23:13 UTC Apr 14\" },\n    \"cron:53c5832a\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"label\": \"Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7\", \"note\": \"completed normally ~23:16 UTC Apr 14 — expected\" },\n    \"main\": { \"status\": \"done\", \"note\": \"ended normally at 00:46 UTC Apr 15 — expected\" },\n    \"telegram:direct:6053576134\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"label\": \"Lead direct\", \"note\": \"running since ~00:55 UTC, last active 01:00 UTC\" },\n    \"telegram:group:-5163901258\": { \"status\": \"running\", \"note\": \"active session, last msg 00:51 UTC Apr 15\" }\n  },\n  \"pipeline\": \"HEALTHY\",\n  \"blockers\": [],\n  \"noChangesSince\": \"2026-04-15T00:51:00Z\"\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":29146,"output":1124,"totalTokens":44627,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":413,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776214918506,"responseId":"062e1687db32e175da6b99c95acf9e88","__openclaw":{"id":"e34a9fbb","seq":5}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Heartbeat state updated. Silent exit — no changes to report."},{"type":"text","text":"Silent exit — no changes since 00:51 UTC. Pipeline stable, 3 cron mon